quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  1,1,"In the name of Allah, the Entirely Merciful, the Especially Merciful"
  1,2,"Praise belongs to God, the Lord of all Being"
  1,3,"the All-merciful, the All-compassionate"
  1,4,the Master of the Day of Doom
  1,5,Thee only we serve; to Thee alone we pray for succour
  1,6,Guide us in the straight path
  1,7,"the path of those whom Thou hast blessed, not of those against whom Thou art wrathful, nor of those who are astray"
